            Two days ago in the Select Committee I asked the Under-Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs, my hon. Friend the Member
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_149wh' title='Col. 149WH &mdash; HC Deb 25 April 2002 vol 384 c149WH' name='column_149wh' href='#column_149wh' rel='bookmark'>149WH</a>
